data.description: $600,000 INDLUDES BOTH PROPERTIES TOGETHER. These are unique properties because they are subdivided into two separate parcels, and each property can be sold independently, or together. Here is how it could save money for both Buyer and Seller (1) A prospective Buyer may wish to make a purchase offer only on the house, parcel number 691-080-008. (2) Or a Buyer may wish to make a purchase offer only on the vacant land next door to the house (which is parcel number 691-080-009). (3) Of course, Buyers can make offers for either or both parcels separately or together. Please call if you have any questions.
